-- Land Minister Says China Home Prices Face Correction, Securities Reports
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-04T23:11:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-04/land-minister-says-china-home-prices-face-correction-securities-reports.html

          
          
             China’s property prices will likely
see a correction in about three months, Securities Times cited
Xu Shaoshi, minister of Land and Resources, as saying.  
 The nation’s current market sales volumes are falling and
prices are stagnant, Xu said, according to the report.  
